\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 An appropriate definition for ontology is given by \\cite\{Guarino:1998wq\} as a \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93logical theory accounting for the intended meaning of a formal vocabulary\u8221\'94.}
