\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 In fact, this is a question of philosophy while ICT is \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93only\u8221\'94 faced with its consequence: computers can deal with language only and have no clue about reality. }
